#------------------------------------------------------------
# Request-level feature gating (shared semantics)
#------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Optional request-level gating for internal / developer features.
#
# Behavior:
# - empty / missing -> allow (default-on)
# - none           -> allow (no conditions)
# - deny_all       -> deny (for everyone)
#
# Supported conditions (AND logic when comma-separated):
# - ip:strict      -> require exact IP match
# - ip:class       -> require CIDR / class-based IP match
# - auth           -> require any authenticated user
# - auth:admin     -> require WordPress admin user
#
# Usage:
#   {FEATURE}_ENABLE_METHOD=
#   {FEATURE}_ENABLE_METHOD=none
#   {FEATURE}_ENABLE_METHOD=deny_all
#   {FEATURE}_ENABLE_METHOD=ip:class
#   {FEATURE}_ENABLE_METHOD=ip:strict
#   {FEATURE}_ENABLE_METHOD=ip:class,auth:admin

